PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 02, TA'AN KWACH'AN COUNCIL, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting in specific areas in the Yukon until April 1, 2007, and (b) repeals a similar Order enacted by Order in Council P.C. 2001-2297 of December 13, 2001.
